  <description>
    <p>Tauon Music Box is a modern, comfortable and streamlined music player for the playback of your local music collection.</p>
    <p>Packed with features while maintaining simplicity. Use drag and drop files for direct and easy file importing. Allows you to manage your music collection with built-in functions such as file renaming, cover art downloading and file deleting.</p>
    <p>Features:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Compatible with most common audio files including MP3, FLAC, APE, TTA, M4A and OGG</li>
      <li>Gapless playback by default</li>
      <li>Built in CUE sheet detection</li>
      <li>Groups tracks by folder</li>
      <li>Easily create and manage playlists</li>
      <li>Lookup artists on Rate Your Music</li>
      <li>Quick and powerful searching</li>
      <li>Create a topchart grid image of your favorite albums</li>
      <li>Scrobble and love tracks to last.fm</li>
      <li>Support for Listenbrainz and launching Musicbrainz Picard</li>
      <li>Monitor your downloads and import archives in one click</li>
      <li>Includes large album art and album gallery layouts</li>
      <li>Transcode folders to dedicated output folder for easy copying to devices</li>
      <li>Support for lyrics, synced lrc files and displaying lyrics with guitar chords</li>
      <li>Multiple preset UI themes to choose from</li>
      <li>Additional mini and micro UI modes</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

